<p>Front page categories allows you to chose what categories appear on your homepage.</p>
<p>The settings can be found in the customizer. You should view the homepage in the customizer for the settings to appear.</p>
<p>By default all categories will display (standard WordPress behaviour). To hide a category untick the box, and it will be removed from your sites homepage. Note: that unticked categories will still display on their respective category archive pages.</p>
